

3 states

follower, leader, candidate

start in follower state

time out become candidate, send 

candidate request vote

nodes reply with vote reply

candidate become leader if majority reply yes

leader send log to followers, followers reply after written

then leader writes to log

leader notifies followers to commit log

nodes have timeout which is amount of time before follower becomes candidate

The election timeout is randomized to be between 150ms and 300ms.

candidate votes for itself, node votes if it hasn't voted in election yet

leader sends logs in intvals of heartbeat timeout

election term continues until follower dosen't receive heartbeat